1476
01:27:02,260 --> 01:27:03,761
也可能被收买
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}they can be bribed.{\r}

1477
01:27:04,387 --> 01:27:07,265
也可能被贿赂
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}They can be bought.{\r}

1478
01:27:08,891 --> 01:27:13,438
然而，机器不会被贿赂
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Machines, however, are corruption free.{\r}

1479
01:27:13,980 --> 01:27:16,149
美国人可以活在一个……
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Americans could be living in a country{\r}

1480
01:27:16,315 --> 01:27:19,652
执法有效率而且没有贪污……
