1481
01:27:19,944 --> 01:27:21,487
的国家
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}but incorruptible.{\r}

1482
01:27:22,780 --> 01:27:25,074
谢谢你，艾利克斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Thank you, Alex, for all you've done.{\r}

1483
01:27:25,241 --> 01:27:26,993
谢谢你做的一切
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}And for all that you are.{\r}

1484
01:27:27,493 --> 01:27:30,663
墨菲警探现在状况危急
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Detective Murphy is currently in critical condition.{\r}

1485
01:27:31,289 --> 01:27:33,833
我们的医生正在全力抢救
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Our doctors are working ceaselessly{\r}

1486
01:27:34,167 --> 01:27:36,919
但目前情况还不明朗
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}but, at this time, it is unclear if he will survive.{\r}

1487
01:27:36,836 --> 01:27:37,962
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(REPORTERS CLAMORING){\r}

1488
01:27:38,171 --> 01:27:41,841
你认为警察涉嫌谋杀墨菲警探
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}KELLY: Ms. Kline, how do you think the attempt{\r}

1489
01:27:40,131 --> 01:27:42,008
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}on Detective Alex Murphy's life{\r}

1490
01:27:42,008 --> 01:27:44,343
是否影响明天的崔佛斯法案表决？
