1491
01:27:44,510 --> 01:27:48,931
我们现在只关心墨菲警探的伤势
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}LIZ: At this time, Omnicorp's sole concern{\r}

1492
01:27:46,429 --> 01:27:48,514
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}is the full recovery of Detective Murphy.{\r}

1493
01:27:49,766 --> 01:27:54,437
墨菲警探要为国捐躯几次才够？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}How many times does Detective Murphy{\r}

1494
01:27:51,893 --> 01:27:54,312
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}have to give his life for his country?{\r}

1495
01:27:55,104 --> 01:27:59,776
希望参议院能投下正确的一票
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I sincerely hope the Senate makes the right vote tomorrow{\r}

1496
01:27:59,942 --> 01:28:04,822
不要让艾利克斯墨菲白白牺牲
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}so that Alex Murphy's sacrifices will not have been in vain.{\r}

1497
01:28:09,368 --> 01:28:11,496
崔佛斯参议员是我的朋友
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}OHIO SENATOR ON TV: Senator Dreyfus is my friend.{\r}

1498
01:28:11,662 --> 01:28:14,373
他是我的导师，在困难时……
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}He has been my mentor and my strength{\r}

1499
01:28:14,540 --> 01:28:17,001
给我支持
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}in times of difficulty on this floor.{\r}

1500
01:28:17,543 --> 01:28:20,546
尽管如此，我服务的是俄亥俄州
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}But despite all that, I work for the state of Ohio,{\r}

1501
01:28:20,713 --> 01:28:23,800
选民的安全是我的优先考量
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}and the safety of its citizens is my top priority.{\r}

1502
01:28:24,175 --> 01:28:25,218
所以我投赞成
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}So I vote yes.{\r}

1503
01:28:25,384 --> 01:28:27,678
崔佛斯法案必须被否决
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}The Dreyfus Act must be repealed.{\r}

1504
01:28:28,054 --> 01:28:30,223
我们以39比10领先
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}That's us ahead, 39 to 10.{\r}

1505
01:28:30,389 --> 01:28:33,226
参议院联络人说我们会获胜
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I spoke to the Senate liaison and it looks like it's in the bag,{\r}

1506
01:28:33,392 --> 01:28:36,479
但和政治人物合作还是要小心
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}but we still have to tread carefully with the politicians.{\r}

1507
01:28:36,395 --> 01:28:37,814
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(NOVAK ELEMENT THEME SONG PLAYING ON TV){\r}

1508
01:28:38,022 --> 01:28:40,066
记者在底特律警局现场连线
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}KELLY: We're here live at DPD headquarters{\r}

1509
01:28:40,233 --> 01:28:43,069
{\an8}刚刚克莱拉墨菲发表声明
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}where moments ago, Clara Murphy made a shocking statement.{\r\an8}

1510
01:28:43,236 --> 01:28:44,320
{\an8}搞什么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}POPE: What the hell?{\r\an8}

1511
01:28:44,487 --> 01:28:49,575
{\an8}欧姆尼不让我们探望艾利克斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Omnicorp has denied me and my son access to Alex for weeks.{\r\an8}

1512
01:28:50,243 --> 01:28:52,078
{\an8}我要求知道真相
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I demand to know why.{\r\an8}

1513
01:28:53,079 --> 01:28:58,084
{\an8}这种处置不人道，有人必须负责
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}This treatment is inhuman and somebody needs to be held accountable.{\r\an8}

1514
01:28:59,252 --> 01:29:01,045
{\an8}我们完蛋了
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Oh, we're fucked.{\r\an8}

1515
01:29:01,212 --> 01:29:04,173
只要再12票，她不会影响投票
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}No, we only need 12 votes.{\r}

1516
01:29:02,547 --> 01:29:04,048
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}She shouldn't make much difference.{\r}

1517
01:29:04,340 --> 01:29:06,551
对，但投票过后呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}POPE: Yeah, but what about after the vote?{\r}

1518
01:29:06,717 --> 01:29:10,930
他们不该见面，要是她影响他……
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I mean, those two should not be allowed contact.{\r}

1519
01:29:08,427 --> 01:29:10,847
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}If she starts putting ideas in his head...{\r}

1520
01:29:11,097 --> 01:29:13,766
带她过来，我来跟她谈
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Bring her in. I'll handle the explanation.{\r}

1521
01:29:13,933 --> 01:29:17,728
艾利克斯呢？不能一直冰冻他
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}POPE: And what about Alex?{\r}

1522
01:29:15,351 --> 01:29:17,603
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You know, unfortunately, we can't just keep him on ice.{\r}

1523
01:29:18,437 --> 01:29:20,857
他在警局开枪吓到一些政治人物
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}LIZ: The shooting at the station spooked some of the politicians.{\r}

1524
01:29:21,023 --> 01:29:23,526
我们必须安抚这些客户
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}They're our clients. We have to take care of them.{\r}

1525
01:29:23,693 --> 01:29:27,029
客户乐见机器降低犯罪率
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}They're fine when a machine is lowering the murder rate,{\r}

1526
01:29:27,196 --> 01:29:30,449
但不希望有人调查贪污
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}but when a man is investigating city politics, they get nervous.{\r}

1527
01:29:30,616 --> 01:29:32,785
首先，他不是人，好吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}All right. First off, it's not a man, okay?{\r}

1528
01:29:32,952 --> 01:29:34,954
它是欧姆尼企业的财产
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}It's property of Omnicorp.{\r}

1529
01:29:35,121 --> 01:29:37,290
再说你根本不用担心政治
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}And politics are the least of your concern.{\r}

1530
01:29:37,456 --> 01:29:39,083
这东西破了自己的谋杀案
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I mean, this thing solved its own murder.{\r}

1531
01:29:39,250 --> 01:29:41,627
难道不会发现我们操控他？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}How long till it realizes you haven't been on the level with it?{\r}

1532
01:29:41,794 --> 01:29:45,798
要是这样记者会争相采访他
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}POPE: If that happens,{\r}

1533
01:29:42,795 --> 01:29:45,715
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}everyjournalist in this country is dying to speak to him.{\r}

1534
01:29:45,965 --> 01:29:47,884
我们创造出一个英雄
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I mean, we created a hero.{\r}

1535
01:29:48,467 --> 01:29:51,137
若他揭发我们就糟了
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}What happens when he opens his mouth?{\r}

1536
01:29:54,640 --> 01:29:56,309
什么比英雄更伟大
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}What's bigger than a hero?{\r}

1537
01:30:07,987 --> 01:30:09,322
死掉的英雄
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Dead hero.{\r}

1538
01:30:13,659 --> 01:30:15,578
叫诺顿过来
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Get me Dr. Norton.{\r}

1539
01:30:24,545 --> 01:30:25,671
你搞什么，雷蒙？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}What is this, Raymond?{\r}

1540
01:30:26,839 --> 01:30:30,843
你派梅托斯监视我\n又骗说他有生命危险？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You have Mattox spying on me and now this bullshit about a "critical condition"?{\r}

1541
01:30:31,010 --> 01:30:33,679
我们都知道艾利克斯没事
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You know and I know Alex is fine!{\r}

1542
01:30:33,846 --> 01:30:35,014
冷静
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Calm down.{\r}

1543
01:30:35,181 --> 01:30:36,682
丹尼
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Bennett.{\r}

1544
01:30:36,849 --> 01:30:39,352
―你的研究太伟大，我不……\n―这跟我的研究无关
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Your work is so good, I don't...{\r}

1545
01:30:38,059 --> 01:30:39,393
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Well, now, this is not about my work!{\r}

1546
01:30:39,518 --> 01:30:41,479
你看见那女人上电视
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You saw the woman on TV!{\r}

1547
01:30:41,646 --> 01:30:43,731
这场闹剧必须停止
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}This has to stop!{\r}

1548
01:30:45,566 --> 01:30:46,859
你是对的
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You're right.{\r}

1549
01:30:47,568 --> 01:30:49,570
但我问你一件事
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}But let me ask you something, Dennett.{\r}

1550
01:30:49,737 --> 01:30:52,073
我们给他什么样的生活？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}What kind of life have we really given Alex Murphy?{\r}

1551
01:30:52,239 --> 01:30:55,701
他永远没办法活得像正常人
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}He's never gonna be a normal man, a father, a husband.{\r}

1552
01:30:55,868 --> 01:30:59,163
等其他机器人上街，他就……
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}By the time we put the other units on the street, he's just...{\r}

1553
01:30:59,330 --> 01:31:00,373
丹尼……
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Bennett.{\r}

1554
01:31:00,873 --> 01:31:02,124
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(SIGHS HEAVILY){\r}

1555
01:31:02,249 --> 01:31:03,751
我们承认吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Let's face it.{\r}

1556
01:31:04,710 --> 01:31:05,920
我们失败了
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}We failed him.{\r}

1557
01:31:07,546 --> 01:31:09,382
我们辜负艾利克斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}We failed Alex Murphy.{\r}

1558
01:31:09,548 --> 01:31:12,718
但我要你顾全大局，这才是重点
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}But I want you to think about the bigger picture{\r}

1559
01:31:11,217 --> 01:31:12,718
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}because that's what we're talking about.{\r}

1560
01:31:12,885 --> 01:31:15,554
你的工作会被研究数十年
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}The work you've done with him is gonna be studied for decades.{\r}

1561
01:31:15,721 --> 01:31:17,890
你改变历史，丹尼
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You've changed the face of history, Dennett.{\r}

1562
01:31:18,057 --> 01:31:22,353
不再有警察因为执行勤务死亡
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}No policeman is ever going to die in the line of duty again{\r}

1563
01:31:23,062 --> 01:31:24,522
全都是因为你
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}because of you.{\r}

1564
01:31:26,273 --> 01:31:27,733
你考虑看看
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You think about that.{\r}

1565
01:31:36,242 --> 01:31:40,121
我要他的家人受到妥善照顾
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I want that family taken care of{\r}

1566
01:31:40,287 --> 01:31:41,706
超过他们的想象
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}beyond their wildest dreams.{\r}

1567
01:31:41,872 --> 01:31:43,916
―我们欠他们的\n―我同意
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}We owe them that. I agree.{\r}

1568
01:31:44,709 --> 01:31:48,045
我要十年的全额资金赞助
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I want full funding. Ten years.{\r}

1569
01:31:48,421 --> 01:31:50,089
新职员，我要自己挑人
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}New staff, all my own people.{\r}

1570
01:31:50,256 --> 01:31:51,799
没问题
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Fantastic.{\r}

1571
01:31:52,717 --> 01:31:53,592
成交
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Deal.{\r}

1572
01:32:03,978 --> 01:32:05,438
怎么回事？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Hey. What's going on?{\r}

1573
01:32:05,604 --> 01:32:07,606
警卫来了，他们要所有人出去
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Security's here. They're clearing everyone out.{\r}

1574
01:32:07,773 --> 01:32:09,233
他们不让他醒来
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}They're not waking him up.{\r}

1575
01:32:09,608 --> 01:32:11,402
不论你做什么，别丢他一个人
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Whatever you do, don't leave him alone.{\r}

1576
01:32:11,569 --> 01:32:12,945
什么叫不让他醒来？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}What do you mean they're not waking him up?{\r}

1577
01:32:13,112 --> 01:32:14,655
（艾利克斯墨菲状况稳定）

1578
01:32:14,822 --> 01:32:18,784
