1579
01:32:16,240 --> 01:32:18,826
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}The clerks have tabulated the results.{\r}

1580
01:32:18,993 --> 01:32:20,953
赞成63票
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}The yeas are 63.{\r}

1581
01:32:21,120 --> 01:32:22,496
反对22票
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}The nays are 22.{\r}

