1585
01:32:30,254 --> 01:32:31,547
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(PEOPLE APPLAUDING){\r}

1586
01:32:34,592 --> 01:32:35,593
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(CELL PHONE RINGING){\r}

1587
01:32:35,801 --> 01:32:38,262
你们动作真慢
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}God, you guys are slow, like a bunch of girls.{\r}

1588
01:32:38,429 --> 01:32:39,430
我是梅托斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}This is Mattox.{\r}

1589
01:32:39,597 --> 01:32:40,848
丹尼同意了
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}SELLARS: Bennett's on board.{\r}

1590
01:32:41,015 --> 01:32:42,475
也该是时候了
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}It's about time.{\r}

1591
01:32:47,688 --> 01:32:48,814
下令吧
