1602
01:33:22,848 --> 01:33:24,016
大卫
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}David.{\r}

1603
01:33:25,684 --> 01:33:27,978
我们要出门，去拿外套
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}We gotta go. Can you grab your coat?{\r}

1604
01:33:27,937 --> 01:33:29,105
