1607
01:33:31,524 --> 01:33:33,025
我要进实验室
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I need access to the lab.{\r}

1608
01:33:33,192 --> 01:33:34,693
不行，他们还在这里
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}That's insane. They're still here.{\r}

1609
01:33:34,860 --> 01:33:36,237
你去引开他们
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Distract them.{\r}

1610
01:33:36,654 --> 01:33:37,696
好
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Okay.{\r}

1611
01:33:38,989 --> 01:33:42,201
―我不能……\n―这里有个女的歇斯底里
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Icannotu{\r}

