1617
01:33:50,042 --> 01:33:52,878
要是有人死掉你负责吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Do you wanna be responsible for the deaths of everyone in this building?{\r}

1618
01:33:53,170 --> 01:33:54,547
站住
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Hey! Stop!{\r}

1619
01:33:54,505 --> 01:33:56,215
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(BREATHING HEAVILY){\r}

1620
01:33:58,551 --> 01:33:59,718
别开枪
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Don't shoot!{\r}

1621
01:33:59,885 --> 01:34:01,262
出来
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Step outside.{\r}

1622
01:34:07,726 --> 01:34:09,395
