{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Alex, can you hear me?{\r}

1632
01:34:36,046 --> 01:34:37,715
这些人要来杀我们
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}These men are here to kill us.{\r}

1633
01:34:37,882 --> 01:34:40,301
他们要来杀我们
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}They're here to kill us, for chrissakes!{\r}

1634
01:34:45,222 --> 01:34:46,807
墨菲女士，昨天晚上……
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}SELLARS: Mrs. Murphy, last night,{\r}

