1636
01:34:49,101 --> 01:34:53,772
他杀了一名同事，然后痉挛发作
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}He killed an unarmed colleague and later suffered a seizure.{\r}

1637
01:34:54,481 --> 01:34:58,986
