{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Very sorry, Mrs. Murphy.{\r}

1640
01:35:02,781 --> 01:35:05,326
我们很快就会发布消息
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}We're going to be making the announcement shortly.{\r}

1641
01:35:05,784 --> 01:35:08,245
你把我关掉，她差点就认罪
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You shut me down. I was about to get a confession.{\r}

1642
01:35:08,913 --> 01:35:10,581
是梅托斯关掉你
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Mattox shut you down.{\r}

1643
01:35:11,916 --> 01:35:14,793
传输器拔掉就不会在发生
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I've removed your transmitter so he won't do it again.{\r}

1644
01:35:15,169 --> 01:35:17,338
塞勒斯不想让你醒来
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Sellars can't afford to wake you up.{\r}

1645
01:35:18,422 --> 01:35:20,507
他派这些人来拔插头
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}He sent these guys to pull the plug.{\r}

1646
01:35:20,966 --> 01:35:24,470
他要你死，你了解吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}He wants you dead, Alex. Do you understand?{\r}

1647
01:35:24,637 --> 01:35:27,932
有什么我们能做的请尽管开口
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Sorry. If there's anything we can do{\r}

1648
01:35:26,472 --> 01:35:27,806
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}for you and David, we'll do it.{\r}

1649
01:35:28,098 --> 01:35:30,184
我不要你的东西
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I want nothing from you.{\r}

1650
01:35:31,143 --> 01:35:32,478
我了解
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I understand.{\r}

1651
01:35:33,020 --> 01:35:35,314
你滚开我们的生活
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You stay out of our lives.{\r}

1652
01:35:36,774 --> 01:35:37,983
你和你的公司都是
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You and your company.{\r}

1653
01:35:38,275 --> 01:35:40,152
如果你希望这样
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}If that's what you think is best.{\r}

1654
01:35:41,111 --> 01:35:42,488
还有一件事
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}There's one more thing.{\r}

1655
01:35:42,655 --> 01:35:45,366
这对大家都好，尤其是大卫
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I think it would be to the benefit of everyone, especially David{\r}

1656
01:35:45,532 --> 01:35:47,785
就是不要公开这件事
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}if we kept this matter private.{\r}

1657
01:35:48,118 --> 01:35:50,663
我们不想破坏艾利克斯的形象
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}We don't wanna damage Alex's legacy.{\r}

1658
01:35:53,207 --> 01:35:55,167
艾利克斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}DR. NORTON'. Alex! Alex!{\r}

1659
01:35:55,459 --> 01:35:57,002
