{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I can fix this!{\r}

1660
01:35:57,169 --> 01:35:58,504
你骗我
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You lied to me.{\r}

1661
01:35:58,671 --> 01:36:01,548
你骗我老婆，你替他们工作
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You lied to my wife.{\r}

1662
01:35:59,922 --> 01:36:01,548
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You're working for the people that are trying to kill me.{\r}

1663
01:36:01,715 --> 01:36:05,135
―你还要我相信你？\n―我可以去找媒体
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}You want me to trust you, Doctor?{\r}

1664
01:36:02,967 --> 01:36:05,010
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Alex, I can go to the press!{\r}

1665
01:36:06,512 --> 01:36:09,139
我可以告诉他们真相
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Alex, I can tell them the whole story!{\r}

1666
01:36:09,390 --> 01:36:10,849
艾利克斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Alex!{\r}

1667
01:36:11,392 --> 01:36:13,352
