{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Listen to me, please!{\r}

1668
01:36:14,353 --> 01:36:17,648
艾利克斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Alex! Alex!{\r}

1669
01:36:29,243 --> 01:36:30,327
搞什么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}What the hell?{\r}

1670
01:36:32,705 --> 01:36:34,415
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(TIRES SCREECHING) (HORNS HONKING){\r}

1671
01:36:38,711 --> 01:36:42,214
