{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}So beautiful.{\r}

1677
01:36:52,683 --> 01:36:55,352
这城市变得多么和平
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}It's become so peaceful.{\r}

1678
