{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I wanna talk to Mr. Sellars.{\r}

1694
01:37:40,397 --> 01:37:41,440
塞勒斯先生
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Mr. Sellars.{\r}

1695
01:37:41,607 --> 01:37:43,609
―直升机还要多久？\n―大概10分钟
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}How close is that helicopter? About 10 minutes, sir.{\r}

1696
