{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}It's an emergency.{\r}

1701
01:38:06,757 --> 01:38:08,342
稍等，塞勒斯先生
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Stand by. Mr. Sellars.{\r}

1702
01:38:08,801 --> 01:38:10,511
克莱拉墨菲要求见你
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Apparently there's a Clara Murphy in the lobby.{\r}

1703
01:38:10,677 --> 01:38:14,014
要是她看见他，计划就泡汤了
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Raymond, if she sees him, we are dead in the water.{\r}

1704
01:38:14,181 --> 01:38:16,517
