{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}What do you wanna do? Bring Mrs. Murphy up here.{\r}

1705
01:38:16,683 --> 01:38:17,810
是，先生
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}MALE SECURITY GUARD: Yes, sir.{\r}

1706
01:38:18,519 --> 01:38:20,145
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(SIRENS WAILING){\r}

1707
01:38:21,688 --> 01:38:24,483
诺顿说他们大楼使用机器人
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Norton said they may be using drones for protection.{\r}

1708
01:38:24,650 --> 01:38:26,693
