{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Clear. Clear.{\r}

1711
01:38:47,005 --> 01:38:48,340
站住
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}MALE SECURITY GUARD: Hold it right there.{\r}

1712
01:38:49,633 --> 01:38:50,342
不要动
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Don't move.{\r}

1713
01:38:53,053 --> 01:38:54,138
{\an8}（模拟处理）

1714
01:38:54,304 --> 01:38:57,474
{\an8}这是私人企业，你无权进入
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}This is private property. You are not authorized to be here!{\r\an8}

1715
01:38:58,851 --> 01:39:00,144
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}(GROANING){\r}

1716
01:39:01,353 --> 01:39:03,689
