{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}I'd put those guns down now if I were you.{\r}

1717
01:39:03,856 --> 01:39:05,524
―放下武器\n―好，我们让开
{\fscx75\fscy75\2c&HFF0000&}Stand down. All right, man, we're good.{\r}

